{"tid":816326,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【港支MPF末日】亞股10連跌 今年累計蒸發5.46萬億","createTime":"2018-09-12T16:08:30.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-12T17:08:26.000Z","uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"e11b188c9bade103c1195e886185baee35e10d7b","tid":816326,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-12T16:08:30.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20180912/58673616\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180912%2F58673616&d=m0dOZuo7z6yUKehDKkSvJJUWI6eGpREPWAa3TRi9Bo4%3D&h=14a1eb53\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180912%2F58673616&h=15fc0ca5\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20180912/58673616</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180912/large/1536749723_8ba1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180912%2Flarge%2F1536749723_8ba1.jpg&h=14f6fad4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nMSCI亞太指數今日已連續第10個交易日下跌，這是自2002年以來、16年最長跌勢，亞股市值今年累計蒸發約7000億美元﹙約54600億港元)。<br />\n<br />\n中美貿易戰、美元強勢、新興市場危機，以及中國股市步入熊市等，都是令亞洲股市連續下跌的因素。摩根士丹利（Morgan Stanley）董事總經理Jonathan Garner認為，亞洲及新興市場的前景仍然悲觀，預計未來幾個月大市會繼續下調，因為中國信貸緊縮，導致經濟放緩，對汽車、科技硬件的需求亦減弱。<br />\n<br />\n今日上證指數再創四年新低，全日跌0.33%，報2,656點；恒指亦續跌0.29%，收報26,345點。"},{"pid":"e4b00ea8c34b6e8c19de365c7827cca76a5ca21f","tid":816326,"uid":128014,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-12T17:05:41.000Z","msg":"一年前已經將90%轉晒落北美<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2cc4c3ccee8067522f58a45f272e9ed002f0e933","tid":816326,"uid":15815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-12T17:07:35.000Z","msg":"一早算撚數🤷🏻&zwj;♂️<br />\n65歲之後都唔知咩世界"},{"pid":"8b7eee4dfe4be56666f18474317b99306de7